Max","iPhone17-iPhone17","iPhoneAir-iPhoneAir","iPadPro11M5-iPadPro11M5","iPadPro11M5Cellular-iPadPro11M5Cellular","iPadPro13M5-iPadPro13M5","iPadPro13M5Cellular-iPadPro13M5Cellular","iPhone17e-iPhone17e","iPadAir11M4-iPadAir11M4","iPadAir11M4Cellular-iPadAir11M4Cellular","iPadAir13M4-iPadAir13M4","iPadAir13M4Cellular-iPadAir13M4Cellular"],"advisories":[],"kind":"software","bundleId":"com.skistar.SKISTAR1","minimumOsVersion":"16.0","formattedPrice":"Free","averageUserRatingForCurrentVersion":4.22051,"averageUserRating":4.22051,"trackCensoredName":"SkiStar","languageCodesISO2A":["DA","EN","DE","NB","SV"],"fileSizeBytes":"243899392","sellerUrl":"https://www.skistar.com/sv/myskistar/appar/","contentAdvisoryRating":"4+","userRatingCountForCurrentVersion":780,"trackViewUrl":"https://apps.apple.com/no/app/skistar/id406481077?uo=4","trackContentRating":"4+","artistId":406481080,"artistName":"SkiStar AB","genres":["Travel"],"price":0.0,"trackId":406481077,"trackName":"SkiStar","primaryGenreName":"Travel","primaryGenreId":6003,"genreIds":["6003"],"releaseDate":"2010-12-08T01:43:06Z","isVppDeviceBasedLicensingEnabled":true,"currentVersionReleaseDate":"2026-06-03T08:39:14Z","sellerName":"Skistar AB","releaseNotes":"We're gearing up for summer in the mountains! \n\nIn this update, we've fixed bugs and sharpened the app – so everything flows as smoothly as a hike across the mountain heaths.\n\nLace up your boots, hop on your bike or just enjoy the view!\n\nAnd hey… more fun news is on the way. Stay tuned!","version":"9.1.25","wrapperType":"software","currency":"NOK","description":"Welcome to the world of SkiStar\n\nHere you can receive information and offers from all our destinations all year round. It's easy to see today's weather and get tips on activities, restaurants and shops. You can also get to know your children's best friend, Valle the Snowman.\n \nBuy winter SkiPass or summer LiftPass cards from the app and pick them up in an automatic dispenser. You can also refill the cards you already have and pay with Swish in Sweden.\n \nMaps will give you a quick overview of open lifts and pistes, as well as biking and hiking trails, and you can also keep track of where your friends are.\n \nYou can see your active booking and everything you need to know about your lodging, your SkiPass/LiftPass, rental products and booked activities.\n \nBy linking your SkiPass, you can collect skiing statistics, chase pins and compete on our leader boards during the winter.\n \nWe wish you a pleasant stay!","userRatingCount":780}